Early ideas for #bloodhound. He was my first task so I mostly carried over the process used on #bumblebee back in 2017. Swipe and you can see the rough sculpts I did in VR to capture attitude/proportion/etc. Then I would paint in details with photoshop. By the end of the show I was blocking in VR then jumped straight to zbrush/maya as it took roughly the same amount of time to sculpt everything. #riseofthebeasts #transformers

@bluebeetle is one of the most enjoyable projects I’ve had the pleasure of working on. Unique experience in that I was able to do a little work on nearly everything while reporting directly to El Hombre @angelmanuelsoto and @jwrickard This was my final proposal for the #bluebeetle costume. The final suit that appeared on screen was done by @david_masson_sg under costume designer @mayescrubeo This was my first real costume design experience so really educational seeing how it evolved through all the artists to fabrication by @ironhead_studio Shout out to Peter Safran for bringing me on board. The film is extremely fun, go see it! #DC
